{"tid":1451299,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反鬼計","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:22:44.000Z","uid":222126,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"209cdd1eea75f4d9327c9b0d6761a2553997e639","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:45:37.000Z","msg":"相信今日大家都同意前線係輸到仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察透過內鬼完美帶風向帶義士送頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係勇武可以暫停但係唔可以終止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>，因為只有衝擊先可以癱瘓政府，阻止邪惡政權運作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟同幾個fd靜落黎之後思考左幾條簡單策略黎化解內鬼招，並希望拋磚引玉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1：凡動員轉場或其他需集體意志之動員均<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必須經大規模理性討論</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />來防止內鬼煽動情緒帶風向送頭。<br />\n<br />\n2：留意耳機。真前線為左隨時了解現場情況一定會打開耳仔聽清楚咩事。冇耳機未必唔係內鬼但係有耳機一定係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3：留意警方對歭及推進時<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突然出現的前線示威者且面容仍然整潔</span></span>。真前線周圍走周圍忙一定身水身汗，唔做野既就會Keep住唔做野唔會無啦啦參與前線。反觀今日銅鑼灣果<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾隻內鬼清場先出現，汗都冇滴</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真前線絕對唔會隨便對手足動手</span></strong>。邊個一出手即刻制服佢，係鬼既機會極大。<br />\n<br />\n5：中場已走得7788既情況下仍然強留其他義士於前線。鬼因為想義士被捕，所以就算形勢極危險仍強留其他義士。<span style=\"color: green;\">真正義士會話：「你想走冇問題，我會守住。」</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而且會係臨被狗完全包圍前一齊走。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以上係我同我fd傾出黎反制內鬼既策略，思路除左係辨識內鬼外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲有阻止內鬼帶風向送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: violet;\">等佢混入黎都做唔到野</span>。內鬼計除左實際帶風向送頭等直接傷害外，最仆街係令到手足與手足間互相懷疑，從而使整個運動互相切割收皮。所以長遠而言，除左不指罵，不篤灰，不割席外仲要制定其他共識，務求內鬼真係完全做唔到野又或者一唔跟共識做野便能辨識。<br />\n<br />\n利申，以上全部發夢內容，切勿當真。"},{"pid":"842457eb179a2eff41f755078a9409a17b8b7477","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d389c095443af31a2921a79b4361162750820035","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa7cf961725c4d98084ab327c966c7bc4afc0f1","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:47:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef7e51e251e65bdaa8874704ebba36070466ce75","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:47:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b31940222dae2c7721badbabf2070a5619b342e","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b74e3dc5ac06707dd6bc6916804f329b05ee8057","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a945f85ccd1c36b961e96f4bffccef2cded7716","tid":1451299,"uid":222126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba70d8a1ee74be97bd83ca09132e35bb31028cd2","tid":1451299,"uid":79039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:29.000Z","msg":"【極重要！！！已BACKUP 】CCTVB 記低左黑警認扮手足<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451073</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-